---
layout: base
title: Blog
permalink: /blog/
description: AI insights, integration tips, and practical guides from the Mobius Integration team.
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Blog</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Practical AI insights — no hype, no fluff. Just what's actually useful for businesses.</p>
    </div>

    {% if collections.post and collections.post.length %}
      <ul class="space-y-10">
        {% for post in collections.post %}
          <li class="border-b border-gray-100 pb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">
                {{ post.data.title }}
              </a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              {{ post.data.excerpt or post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(180) }}
            </p>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="inline-block mt-4 text-indigo-600 font-semibold text-sm hover:underline">
              Read more &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    {% else %}
      <div class="text-center py-16 text-gray-500">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✍️</div>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Posts coming soon.</p>
        <p>We're putting together practical AI guides for businesses. Check back shortly.</p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-6 text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
</section>
